Look, seriously bud, your heart seems to be in the right place so I would soonest see you enjoy your EQ peacefully, but it's become clear to me over a number of your posts that you really have no clue about a lot of major aspects of the game.  When you declared it was unreasonable and absurd to sell bone chips in the bazaar for 2 gold per because that's a 2000% mark-up over what a merchant will pay....  Look, that's a mainstay of the EQ economy.  It happens everywhere, on every server, for some very good reasons.  And as for using vendor prices as an indication....just try to sell some major piece of your equipment to a vendor sometime and see what he offers, 'kay?<br>
